'''2014年首爾地鐵追撞'''，或称'''上往十里站追尾事故'''（{{kor|k=상왕십리역 추돌 사고|hanja=上往十里驛追突事故}}），是指2014年5月2日下午3時32分時，於[[大韓民國|大韓民國]][[首爾特別市|首爾特別市]][[城東區_(首爾)|城東區]]的[[首都圈電鐵|首都圈電鐵]][[首爾地鐵2號線|2號線]][[上往十里站|上往十里站]]發生之列車[[追撞|追撞]]事故。後來[[韩国检察厅|地方检察官]]判定388人受傷（24人重傷），<ref name="prosecutor indict">{{cite news|title=388명 부상 ‘상왕십리역 추돌사고’, 9개월만에 밝혀진 원인은?|newspaper=[[東亞日報|東亞日報]]|trans-title=388 people were injured in the Sangwangsimni Station crash. What was the cause of the crash happened nine months ago?|date=2021-02-01|last=박성진|url=https://www.donga.com/news/Society/article/all/20150201/69419250/1|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210527031326/https://www.donga.com/news/Society/article/all/20150201/69419250/1|archivedate=2021-05-27|accessdate=2021-05-27}}</ref>而當初媒體報導僅238人受傷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E8%BF%BD%E6%92%9E%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-170%E9%A4%98%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7-081200273.html |title=TVBS：首爾地鐵追撞意外　170餘人傷 |accessdate=2014-05-02 |archive-date=2014-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503013300/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E8%BF%BD%E6%92%9E%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-170%E9%A4%98%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7-081200273.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rt">{{cite web|author=|title=Over 200 injured as two trains collide in Seoul subway|trans_title=首尔地铁相撞 200余人受伤|url=http://rt.com/news/156336-south-korea-train-collision/|publisher=[[今日俄罗斯|今日俄罗斯]]|date=2014-05-02|accessdate=2014-05-03|language=en|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715190356/http://rt.com/news/156336-south-korea-train-collision/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这一事故仅发生在造成约300人遇难和失踪的[[世越号沉没事故|世越号沉没事故]]后不久。<ref name="reuters"/>

==事發==
2014年5月2日15时30分，停靠於[[首爾地鐵2號線|首爾地鐵2號線]][[上往十里站|上往十里站]]的2260次列車遭到後方開往[[蠶室站|蠶室站]]方面的2258次列車追撞。造成前車後兩節車廂脫軌。事件造成约238人受伤，但无人重伤，<ref name="rt"/><ref name="reuters">{{cite web|first=Jack|last=Kim|first2=Kahyun|last2=Yang|title=Subway trains crash in South Korean capital, 200 people hurt|trans_title=韩国首都发生地铁相撞事故，200人受伤|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/05/02/us-southkorea-crash-idUSBREA4105S20140502|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2014-05-02|accessdate=2014-05-02|language=en|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713175452/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/05/02/us-southkorea-crash-idUSBREA4105S20140502|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中32人被送往附近的医院接受救治。<ref name="ap"/>事發後，首爾地鐵2號線[[乙支路入口站|乙支路入口站]]至[[聖水站|聖水站]]之間暫時停止運行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E8%BF%BD%E6%92%9E-%E5%B9%B8%E7%84%A1%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%A1-085605862.html |title=中央通訊社(CNA)：首爾地鐵追撞 幸無嚴重傷亡 |accessdate=2014-05-02 |archive-date=2014-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503020056/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E8%BF%BD%E6%92%9E-%E5%B9%B8%E7%84%A1%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%A1-085605862.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

据目击者称，许多乘客忽视地铁中要求其留在车厢内的通告，而是强行打开车门、逃离到了轨道上。<ref name="bbc">{{cite web|author=|title=South Korea subway crash injures dozens in Seoul|trans_title=韩国首尔地铁相撞造成多人受伤|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27250961|publisher=[[BBC新闻|BBC新闻]]|date=2014-05-02|accessdate=2014-05-02|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505210252/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-27250961|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[YTN|YTN]]电视台报道称由于地铁脱轨，乘客离开列车后沿着轨道步行了一小段距离才回到车站。一名负责应急的政府官员说，许多乘客在从地铁车厢跳入轨道的过程中受伤。<ref name="reuters"/> [[韩国联合通讯社|韩国联合通讯社]]称前一列地铁在遭到另一列撞击之后由于机械故障而急停，<ref name="bbc"/>且事故有可能是移动“列车自动距离控制系统”操作失败而导致的。<ref name="ap">{{cite web|author=|title=Seoul subway trains crash, causing minor injuries|trans_title=首尔地铁相撞 乘客轻微受伤|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/south-korean-media-subway-accident-injures-dozens/2014/05/02/3c051eb0-d1cf-11e3-a714-be7e7f142085_story.html|publisher=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|work=[[美联社|美联社]]|date=2014-05-02|accessdate=2014-05-02|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502120658/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/south-korean-media-subway-accident-injures-dozens/2014/05/02/3c051eb0-d1cf-11e3-a714-be7e7f142085_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
